Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《人间失格》发表于昭和23年（1948年）6月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧随其后的6月16日 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举世震惊的消息传来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太宰治自杀身亡 享年38岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下“写不下去了”的遗书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发表作品后随即自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且从其内容来看 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《人间失格》亦被视为太宰治的自传体小说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其主人公叶藏与太宰的确有许多共通点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身世 女性 毒品 酗酒 自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛作为其佐证 还有一张照片流传于世 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太宰少年时代所拍摄的全家福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片中他笑得格外灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其他家人的表情格格不入 独自展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笑容背后仿佛隐藏着苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因名作 更显青涩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:00:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 人间失格第二话

Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从孩提时代起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直在讨好周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 阿叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我对他人充满了恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此我想到的招数 就是逗笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我对人类最后的求爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠逗笑这一根细线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勉强保住了与人类的一丝联系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上我不断地强装笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心却是拼死拼活 汗流浃背地为人民服务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装的 装的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丑的演技被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 让我共一下伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 傻气会传染的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没带伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很近 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二话 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严重的耳脓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雨水渗进去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让女人着迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别跟人家说我坏话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家常说我可爱 帅气或是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可从来没人说我是怪物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看到真相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道自己是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大庭…叶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶藏 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊吩咐我照顾你今后的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这副样子会影响议员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊说要坚决与你断绝父子关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于对方的遗属
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是用钱打发掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗属？你说打发是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人姓甚名谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后我得去找她的遗属了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军部在大陆的暗中活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本政府为摆脱萧条
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵略大陆的意图是明摆着的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年张作霖被炸死的事件正是日军的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该更清楚地让读者知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种报道谁会有兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这个人快出院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去采访他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女人殉情却自己生还
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只让女人死了的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是事故 有杀人嫌疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有伪装成殉情 故意杀人的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就是顶风臭四十里的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太们就喜欢这种报道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在镰仓医院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镰仓…您让我现在就去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头我帮你去说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人说不定就喜欢半老徐娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种有几分姿色的大姐去采访
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会说点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 我家孩子在等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说女人就是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合同到期就给我走人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多古助 你给我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是承蒙您照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么搞的 多危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 茂子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在画什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他会在天堂一直保佑小茂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 给你做甜甜的炸面包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉


Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在店里见了女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻钻进她裙底了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么感觉…就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没闻过的肉感的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得死而无憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就殉情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐血痰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是结核
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回局里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审讯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说得没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条子太容易打发了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来可得帮我个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 特别专访
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上镜费要先付
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 瞧这目中无人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准干得出来 做掉女人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是个帅哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人定是一见钟情的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 志津子小姐也会一见钟情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是个孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这傻女人说也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 他的采访呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扯什么借口来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是殉情失败
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我不可能杀那位女士”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯都不会承认自己是杀人犯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受害人遗属呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收钱了吧 守口如瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿被杀了还守口如瓶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大庭氏对少爷的照片登了报纸的事甚为恼怒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是会影响议员生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一没看着你就被人拍了照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要不要我今后管你生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定拿了你老爸给的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把那些钱转给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 没忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止可都是我一直在照顾他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织那边我帮你退会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的好意 感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊委托我监视你 以免你再自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校那边办了主动退学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点不自由 你就忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出去 那我该做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事看看杂志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但重复同样的事 也未免太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有怪物的画哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物的画？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是梵高的自画像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪物的画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这画的是怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵高是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可从没想到过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也要画怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 可以画怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日芝加哥市场已被封锁 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而世界经济混乱依然不见好转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国也将有众多公司倒闭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我 这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是能转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是能转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能活得像个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物不能活在人类的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后要活得像个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来取原稿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 插图已经画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等哦 请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀未遂的人还喝什么茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那啥 他其实和女的殉情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却自己一个人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个善良的艺术家 交友甚广
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这种落后于时代的作家同行也无法见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是镰仓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来您知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么不想依靠我 却又厚着脸皮跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半也没别的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不用追上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来好像走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就爱用这招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被他骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀木说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么想活得像个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单凭一己之力却什么也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没地方住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家过的也不是人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁 万岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧


